title: Finding Your Why
itunes:title: Finding Your Why
description:
In this special bonus class I'm teaching you how to find your why for weightloss. It's not what you've always been taught. Knowing why you want to lose your weight gives a chance to stop eating at the moment all you want to do is stuff your face.

At the end I tell you all about The No BS Weightloss Program. Click here for more information. www.joinnobs.com

Membership is open ONLY from September 16 - September 19, 11:59pm CST.
